'''Qubes OS'''是一个{{le|安全操作系统|Security-focused operating system|专注于安全}}的桌面[[操作系统|操作系统]]，旨在通过隔离提供[[计算机安全|安全保障]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.theregister.co.uk/2012/09/05/qubes_secure_os_released/|title=Qubes OS bakes in virty system-level security|publisher=[[The_Register|The Register]]|date=September 5, 2012|accessdate=2020-05-16|archive-date=2019-08-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190820190244/https://www.theregister.co.uk/2012/09/05/qubes_secure_os_released/|dead-url=no}}</ref>通过[[Xen|Xen]]来执行[[虚拟化|虚拟化]]，用户环境可以基于[[Fedora_(作業系統)|Fedora]]、[[Debian|Debian]]、[[Whonix|Whonix]]和[[Microsoft_Windows|Microsoft Windows]]或其他操作系统。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.qubes-os.org/doc/Templates/|title=Qubes OS Templates|accessdate=2020-05-16|archive-date=2020-04-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200423185422/https://www.qubes-os.org/doc/templates/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.qubes-os.org/doc/WindowsAppVms/|title=Installing and using Windows-based AppVMs|accessdate=2020-05-16|archive-date=2019-02-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190220110209/https://www.qubes-os.org/doc/WindowsAppVms/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2014年2月16日，Qubes荣获2014年端点安全解决方案创新奖。

==安全目标==
Qubes通过隔离来保障安全性，<ref>{{cite web|url=http://theinvisiblethings.blogspot.com/2008/09/three-approaches-to-computer-security.html|title=The three approaches to computer security|publisher=Joanna Rutkowska|date=September 2, 2008|accessdate=2020-05-17|archive-date=2020-02-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200229040455/http://theinvisiblethings.blogspot.com/2008/09/three-approaches-to-computer-security.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>并假设不可能有完美的、无漏洞的桌面环境。因为桌面环境有数百万行的代码并与数十亿的软件/硬件密切相关。这些关联中的任何一个关键错误都可能足以让[[恶意软件|恶意软件]]控制计算机。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.tomshardware.com/reviews/qubes-os-joanna-rutkowska-windows,3009.html|title=Qubes OS: An Operating System Designed For Security|publisher=Tom's hardware|date=August 30, 2011}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.economist.com/blogs/babbage/2014/03/computer-security|title=A digital fortress?|publisher=The Economist|date=March 28, 2014|accessdate=2020-05-17|archive-date=2017-12-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171229112228/https://www.economist.com/blogs/babbage/2014/03/computer-security|dead-url=no}}</ref>

为了保护桌面计算机的安全，Qubes隔离了各种操作环境，因此，如果其中一个操作环境被入侵，恶意软件只能得到该环境内的数据。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.wired.com/2014/11/protection-from-hackers|title=How Splitting a Computer Into Multiple Realities Can Protect You From Hackers|publisher=Wired|date=November 20, 2014|accessdate=2020-05-17|archive-date=2017-02-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170216012252/https://www.wired.com/2014/11/protection-from-hackers/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

在Qubes中，有两个层面的隔离：硬件控制器被隔离到功能域（图形界面、网络、存储），而用户的数字生活由不同的信任级别隔离。例如：工作域（信任度最高）、购物域、随机域（信任度最低）<ref>{{cite web|url=http://theinvisiblethings.blogspot.com/2011/03/partitioning-my-digital-life-into.html|publisher=Joanna Rutkowska|title=Partitioning my digital life into security domains|date=March 13, 2011|accessdate=2020-05-17|archive-date=2020-04-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200421220236/http://theinvisiblethings.blogspot.com/2011/03/partitioning-my-digital-life-into.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。每个域都在独立的[[虚拟机|虚拟机]]中运行。

Qubes不是一个[[多用户|多用户]]系统。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://groups.google.com/forum/#!msg/qubes-devel/XnTly2JNfPw/BppN_D5vn4kJ|title=Google Groups - Qubes as a multi-user system|last=Rutkowska|first=Joanna|date=May 3, 2010|website=Google Groups|publisher=|access-date=|archive-date=2011-01-22|archive-url=http://arquivo.pt/wayback/20110122130054/https://groups.google.com/forum/#!msg/qubes-devel/XnTly2JNfPw/BppN_D5vn4kJ|dead-url=no}}</ref>

